#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.90"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.90:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.90:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga "
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.90:0.3"
msgid "90. Dutiyasekhasutta "
msgstr "90. A Trainee (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.90:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“These five things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

msgctxt "an5.90:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.90:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu bahukicco hoti bahukaraṇīyo viyatto kiṅkaraṇīyesu; "
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant trainee has many duties and responsibilities, and is competent in many tasks. "

msgctxt "an5.90:1.4"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the first thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.90:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu appamattakena kammena divasaṃ atināmeti; "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee spends their day doing trivial work. "

msgctxt "an5.90:2.2"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the second thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.117, sc3
msgctxt "an5.90:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu saṃsaṭṭho viharati gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena; "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee mixes closely with laypeople and renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson. "

msgctxt "an5.90:3.2"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the third thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an5.90:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu akālena gāmaṃ pavisati, atidivā paṭikkamati; "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee enters the town at the wrong time, and returns too late in the day. "

msgctxt "an5.90:4.2"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fourth thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

# NOTE: Note that BB has “gets to hear”, but sotum is not in the text. katha is often not just passive listening but engaging in conversation.
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an5.90:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu yāyaṃ kathā ābhisallekhikā cetovivaraṇasappāyā, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t get to take part in talk about self-effacement that helps open the heart, when they want, without trouble or difficulty. That is, "

#. VAR: akicchalābhī na akasiralābhī → kicchalābhī kasiralābhī (bj, s1-3, km pī)
msgctxt "an5.90:5.2"
msgid "appicchakathā santuṭṭhikathā pavivekakathā asaṃsaggakathā vīriyārambhakathā sīlakathā samādhikathā paññākathā vimuttikathā vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, evarūpiyā kathāya na nikāmalābhī hoti na akicchalābhī na akasiralābhī; "
msgstr "talk about fewness of wishes, contentment, seclusion, aloofness, arousing energy, ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and vision of freedom. "

msgctxt "an5.90:5.3"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fifth thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.90:5.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These five things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an5.90:6.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These five things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

msgctxt "an5.90:6.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.90:6.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na bahukicco hoti na bahukaraṇīyo viyatto kiṅkaraṇīyesu; "
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant trainee doesn’t have many duties and responsibilities, even though they are competent in many tasks. "

msgctxt "an5.90:6.4"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:6.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the first thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an5.90:7.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na appamattakena kammena divasaṃ atināmeti; "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t spend their day doing trivial work. "

msgctxt "an5.90:7.2"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:7.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the second thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.118, sc8
msgctxt "an5.90:8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu asaṃsaṭṭho viharati gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena; "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t mix closely with laypeople and renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson. "

msgctxt "an5.90:8.2"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:8.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the third thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an5.90:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na atikālena gāmaṃ pavisati, nātidivā paṭikkamati; "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t enter the village too early or return too late in the day. "

msgctxt "an5.90:9.2"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:9.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fourth thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an5.90:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu yāyaṃ kathā ābhisallekhikā cetovivaraṇasappāyā, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee gets to take part in talk about self-effacement that helps open the heart, when they want, without trouble or difficulty. That is, "

msgctxt "an5.90:10.2"
msgid "appicchakathā santuṭṭhikathā pavivekakathā asaṃsaggakathā vīriyārambhakathā sīlakathā samādhikathā paññākathā vimuttikathā vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, evarūpiyā kathāya nikāmalābhī hoti akicchalābhī akasiralābhī; "
msgstr "talk about fewness of wishes, contentment, seclusion, aloofness, arousing energy, ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and vision of freedom. "

msgctxt "an5.90:10.3"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ. "
msgstr "They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart. "

msgctxt "an5.90:10.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fifth thing that doesn't lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.90:10.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These five things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.90:10.6"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.90:10.7"
msgid "Theravaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an5.90:11.1"
msgid "Rajanīyo vītarāgo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.2"
msgid "kuhakāssaddhaakkhamā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.3"
msgid "Paṭisambhidā ca sīlena, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.4"
msgid "thero sekhā pare duveti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
